"Cuando selecciona un  :guilabel:`Ticket`, Odoo muestra el formulario "
"detallado del mismo.  "

#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/overview/help_center.rst:85
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Knowledge (book)` icon, located above the chatter to "
